{
    "id": "3dprinter/start",
    "title": "Set up your first 3D printer",
    "description": "Accept Sydney's offer of a 3D printer, and learn how to set it up for use in your space exploration adventure.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/first_3d_printer_setup.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/sydney.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Sydney here. dChat sent me. I can outfit you with a 3D printer—ready to own one?",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "enthusiastic",
                    "text": "A 3D printer? That sounds amazing! Tell me more."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "enthusiastic",
            "text": "Good. It prototypes parts fast, prints fixtures, and keeps you moving. I've already assembled and calibrated it. You in?",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "grant",
                    "text": "I say let's do this!!"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "grant",
            "text": "Step one: accept the printer. I tossed in filament too. PLA melts hot and lays down one layer at a time—slow at first, faster once you tune it. This is a starter model; upgrades exist when you're ready.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "8aa6dc27-dc42-4622-ac88-cbd57f48625f",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "d3590107-25ff-4de5-af3a-46e2497bfc52",
                            "count": 1000
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Don't mind if I do!"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "benchy",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "8aa6dc27-dc42-4622-ac88-cbd57f48625f",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "d3590107-25ff-4de5-af3a-46e2497bfc52",
                            "count": 1000
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "I've got the goods! What's next?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "benchy",
            "text": "First print: Benchy. It's the baseline boat test. Once it prints clean, your setup is ready. It'll take a bit—grab a coffee while it runs.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "3dprint-benchy",
                    "text": "Ok, here goes nothing!"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "7892ffc6-c651-445f-946b-7edc998cf389",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "I've printed the Benchy! What's next?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "Nice work. You're cleared to print mission gear (and whatever else). Ping me for troubleshooting. Here's a little dUSD—dChat can help you earn more.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Thanks, Sydney! I appreciate your help. And I'll keep that in mind!"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
